When used in the context of rage comics, it is usually preceded by a stick-figure drawing of the same man humming and walking with sunglasses still on.

NoNutNovember ($NNN) tokenizes the classic November challenge and makes it a social, on-chain game of discipline. Buy $NNN, lock in the first week of November to start a personal 30-day run, and let transparent, verifiable actions decide your outcome. Public accountability, simple rules, real bragging rights.

How to play:
- Buy $NNN (trading live before Nov 1).
- Lock during the first week of November to start your 30-day timer.
- Finish your run, then mint your badge (NFT).

Your path (on-chain):
- Hero — hold your lock to the end.
- Fallen Brother — burn to confess during your run.
- Loser — unlock early.

* Precedence: any burn marks Fallen; any early unlock/transfer marks Loser; holding to the end marks Hero.

Badges & rarity:
- Every path mints a badge in our yearly collection (NNN Challenge 2025).
- Rarity scales with how much you lock.
- Finish Hero and burn instead of unlocking to earn the optional Ascetic bonus trait.
- Leaderboards and a Fallen feed make standings and confessions public and fun to follow.

We’re building a supportive, meme-powered community around discipline, focus, and good habits—entertainment-first; not advice. Over time, we want NNN to grow into a hub for men’s health, bringing in experts and coaches to share guidance on discipline and well-being. The challenge returns every November with a fresh edition and a new NFT collection.
